{"tid":1211550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣稱明天集會遭警方反對　繼續呼籲市民罷工罷市","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:07:04.000Z","uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3541acc29d1b4ed37469d9813663288fdd432cb4","tid":1211550,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"岑子杰表示，未來民陣的行動仍要進一步思考，會盡快作公布。（張浩賢攝）<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰表示，明天的集會已遭警方反對，但會繼續呼籲市民罷工罷市。<br />\n<br />\n他批評特首林鄭月娥，一方面說關心年輕人，但另一方面卻容許警方以催淚彈及像膠子彈射學生，有人受傷滿面鮮血。他又說，今日是和平集會，參與人士手無寸鐵，卻被指是暴動，又反指是警方以非常不對等的武力驅散示威。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰表示，未來民陣的行動仍要進一步思考，會盡快作公布。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462474-20190612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462474-20190612.htm&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=8a2ba3fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462474-20190612.htm&h=347ba454\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462474-20190612.htm</a>"},{"pid":"211a21a52ce2d33b90ff11e1667c796f54653db6","tid":1211550,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警 祝黑警全家俾車撞到變植物人啦"},{"pid":"b10bfa5ae64e2771f337d4d94ca87af3977216b5","tid":1211550,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}